      "orig": "/L50189 Natural Gas Upgrading - Separex membrane systems remove carbon dioxide and water vapor to pipeline specifications and lower the H 2 S level. Systems can be installed either onshore or offshore, at the wellhead or at gathered facilities.",
      "text": "/L50189 Natural Gas Upgrading - Separex membrane systems remove carbon dioxide and water vapor to pipeline specifications and lower the H 2 S level. Systems can be installed either onshore or offshore, at the wellhead or at gathered facilities.",
