          "charspan": [
            0,
            514
          ]
        }
      ],
      "orig": "UOP offers complete membrane system design including new robust and comprehensive feed pretreatment schemes to extend membrane life. Improved pretreatment, in combination with the continuing development of advanced membranes, has even further enhanced the reliability and performance of membrane technology and made it the CO 2 removal technology of choice in a variety of processing conditions. As with all our processes, service is always readily available through UOP's worldwide technical service organization.",
      "text": "UOP offers complete membrane system design including new robust and comprehensive feed pretreatment schemes to extend membrane life. Improved pretreatment, in combination with the continuing development of advanced membranes, has even further enhanced the reliability and performance of membrane technology and made it the CO 2 removal technology of choice in a variety of processing conditions. As with all our processes, service is always readily available through UOP's worldwide technical service organization."
    },
